      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">3</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Services Compared</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">$7+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Starting Price</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">FDA</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Approved</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">3-6mo</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">See Results</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison Section -->
  <section id="comparison" class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
          Service Comparison
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600">
          Updated {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', year: 'numeric' })}
        </p>
      </div>

      <ComparisonTable brands={brands} location="hair-health-table" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Treatment Options -->
  <section id="treatments" class="section-light">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 text-center">
        Hair Loss Treatment Options
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        FDA-approved medications proven to stop hair loss and promote regrowth.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
              üíä
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Finasteride</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Oral Medication (Propecia)</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Blocks DHT, the hormone that causes male pattern baldness. Take daily. 80-90% of users maintain or regrow hair. Most effective treatment available.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">Pricing:</div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Keeps: $7-20/month</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Hims: $25-40/month</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Ro: $30-50/month</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6 ring-2 ring-brand-accent">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
              üß¥
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900">Minoxidil</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Topical Solution (Rogaine)</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Stimulates blood flow to hair follicles. Apply twice daily. Works best for crown/top of head. Often combined with finasteride for best results.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">Pricing:</div>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Keeps: $15-25/month</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Hims: $15-30/month</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Ro: $20-35/month</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">
            Combination therapy (finasteride + minoxidil) provides best results
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">
        Common Questions
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group card p-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900">
            <span>How long until I see results?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-accent">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Most users see noticeable results in 3-6 months. Hair loss should slow or stop within the first few months, with regrowth becoming visible around 6-12 months. Consistency is key - these medications work best when taken daily.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group card p-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900">
            <span>Are there side effects?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-accent">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Finasteride side effects are rare (2-4% of users) and may include decreased libido or erectile dysfunction. Minoxidil may cause scalp irritation or unwanted facial hair growth. Most users experience no side effects. Always consult with a healthcare provider.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group card p-6">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-900">
            <span>Do I need to use these medications forever?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-brand-accent">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, these medications require ongoing use to maintain results. If you stop treatment, hair loss will resume within 6-12 months. Think of it like managing any chronic condition - consistent treatment is necessary for continued benefits.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Content -->
  <section class="section-light border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 text-center">
        Explore More Categories
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/sexual-health" class="card-hover p-6 group">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•</div>
